{"tid":326032,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得只要過得開心就得？","createTime":"2017-07-17T15:57:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T17:56:57.000Z","uid":19502,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3786e7d6566d3e1640ca867d4b19ed35c7a14d3e","tid":326032,"uid":19502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T15:57:17.000Z","msg":"有時係到諗<br />\n萬一真係過得唔開心好一段時間<br />\n咪自殺死囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係咁唔開心嘅咁生存黎做乜<br />\nbtw我依家過得好充實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc06aa0ac0827d378b642b9610bb1e8693668edd","tid":326032,"uid":13293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:01:42.000Z","msg":"有，成日覺得周遭氛圍既人和事物好煩，好想離開呢到，自己一個人去個無人認識自己既地方生活，一定會過得開心好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a782a54f782ce52b648688f325a2ffb752198733","tid":326032,"uid":19502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:03:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有，成日覺得周遭氛圍既人和事物好煩，好想離開呢到，自己一個人去個無人認識自己既地方生活，一定會過得開心好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有錢就好 我都想離開香港生活<br />\n同你一樣"},{"pid":"b4919c9cc8a9a8136db33664519e264c40d4a35e","tid":326032,"uid":19502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:15:09.000Z","msg":"所以我唔明啲人儲錢黎做乜<br />\n如果自己死咗咪冇得用"},{"pid":"a2fce36643e02053549d5b5c17dee9beafdde376","tid":326032,"uid":7915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:39:56.000Z","msg":"有諗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但依家唔想死住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd3e4a255f840eb496317b883e44892535a0e7d","tid":326032,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:42:40.000Z","msg":"冇諗到自殺個part 但如果連最基本既開心都冇 好無謂"},{"pid":"958c47d631d74d8fad476d86