":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:22:33.000Z","msg":"好想時光倒流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8020368009bf5fda1501eeca203046372e8f6ee7","tid":326032,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:22:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>覺 開心緊要過好多嘢 人冇咗快樂形同行屍走肉</blockquote><br />\n係㗎所以有人供樓供到好想死 我自己真係喺度諗點解你唔死呢 <br />\n或者點解唔用啲錢黎做啲開心嘅嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同感 成日覺得話唔定一陣撞車死咗 所以一直抱住是旦啦使咩咁緊張嘅心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd817bc87b4ba6c11d0a145625434fc9dff1c48e","tid":326032,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:28:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冇諗到自殺個part 但如果連最基本既開心都冇 好無謂</blockquote><br />\n 我都覺啊所以我真心覺得做人最緊要開心</blockquote><br />\n唔開心唔會持續一世 開心都一樣<br />\n你點判斷唔開心既時候幾時死</blockquote><br />\n你都講得啱嘅不過我覺得覺得絕望嗰陣就應該要死囉 <br />\n可能我自己比較現實我覺得做人唔開心<br />\n不如死咗佢好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我又未諗到咁極端 始終一死就代表放棄左將來幾十年既可能性 <br />\n一諗到呢步就會卻步</blockquote><br />\n你確保你幾十年會係成功嘅 ￼</blockquote><br />\n當然唔得 不過換個角度 如果你已經知道哂將來既事 可能會比你唔開心更加想死"},{"pid":"dfbe53323cb2f67047a7d5ae6f0777e0a05a8e76","tid":326032,"uid":52512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:28:11.000Z","msg":"點樣開心先係學問。"},{"pid":"6497be0adfa44ec2f91e877ffda533c8fad2a193","tid":326032,"uid":7915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:39:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有諗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但依家唔想死住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解唔想死因為Ricky屋企人？</blockquote><br />\n其一<br />\n同埋我重想睇下個世界<br />\n係生活喺香港唔開心姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58db8500532a96aae3c2585dc1be5877e6df54e","tid":326032,"uid":7915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:40:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想時光倒流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd86abc3465dfc9a13e2e9e19336e5109ce96a2","tid":326032,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:42:59.000Z","msg":"起香港壓力真係好大<br />\n讀書大壓力,讀得唔好學歷差就演變成將來經濟壓力<br />\n甚至屋企家景本身唔好已經要早D出來打工搵錢,直接影響埋學業<br />\n<br />\n普通人就算經濟能力夠三餐,住屋又成問題<br />\n當你好彩搵到公屋住<br />\n家人或者自己第日有重病,普通人經濟能力無可能AFFORD到<br />\n<br />\n已經諗定自己第日如果重病會自殺算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}